highlights.text: “Excuses” by AP Dhillon, Gurinder Gill, and Intense has been on Top Songs Delhi the longest, at 54 weeks straight.
“Unholy (feat. Kim Petras)” by Sam Smith and Kim Petras is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Delhi, up 20 spots at #30.
AP Dhillon has the most spots on Top Songs Delhi. “Summer High” is the highest at #3.
“Ainak” by Gulab Sidhu and Sukh Lotey is the highest new entry on Top Songs Delhi at #23.
